sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as 用户
    participant H as HomeTab(搜索框)
    participant AS as AppStorage
    participant SRP as SearchResultPage
    participant API as api.ets(searchPosts)
    participant R as PostsRoute(GET /v1/posts)
    participant S as postService.listPosts
    participant DB as Prisma/MySQL

    Note over H: 首页搜索框 onSubmit（原 toast 占位 → 改为跳转）
    U->>H: 输入关键词并回车
    H->>H: this.searchKeyword = 输入值
    H->>AS: setOrCreate('searchKeyword', keyword)
    H->>SRP: router.pushUrl({url:'pages/SearchResultPage'})

    Note over SRP: aboutToAppear 初始化
    SRP->>AS: get('searchKeyword') → keyword
    SRP->>SRP: searchText = keyword; refresh()

    rect rgb(235,245,255)
    Note over SRP,DB: 首屏加载（refresh → fetch(reset=true)）
    SRP->>API: searchPosts({keyword, page:1, limit:10, sort:'latest'})
    API->>R: GET /v1/posts?keyword=..&page=1&limit=10&sort=latest
    R->>S: listPosts({keyword, page, limit, sort})
    S->>DB: findMany({where:{status:1, OR:[title/content/genre/tags 包含 kw]}, orderBy, skip, take})
    S->>DB: count({where})
    DB-->>S: [rows, total]
    S-->>R: {list, pagination:{page,limit,total}}
    R-->>API: {code:0, data:{list, pagination}}
    API-->>SRP: ListResult<Post>
    SRP->>SRP: posts = res.list; total = res.pagination.total
    SRP->>SRP: finished = (res.list.length < limit)
    SRP-->>U: 渲染 2 列 PostCard 网格 + "共找到 N 篇"
    end

    Note over SRP,U: 滚动到底加载更多
    U->>SRP: 上滑（onScrollIndex 末项可见）
    SRP->>SRP: loadMore(): if(!finished&&!loading){page++; fetch(false)}
    SRP->>API: searchPosts({keyword, page:2, ...})
    API->>R: GET /v1/posts?keyword=..&page=2...
    R->>S: listPosts(...)
    S->>DB: findMany(skip=limit, take=limit)
    DB-->>S: 下一页 rows
    S-->>API: {list, pagination}
    API-->>SRP: ListResult<Post>
    SRP->>SRP: posts = posts.concat(res.list)

    Note over SRP,U: 点击卡片跳详情（复用 HomeTab 的父级包裹点击模式，不改 PostCard）
    U->>SRP: 点击某 PostCard
    SRP->>AS: setOrCreate('detailPostId', id) + setDetailPostId(id)
    SRP->>SRP: router.pushUrl({url:'pages/DetailPage'})

    Note over SRP,U: 失败态重试（P1-3）
    SRP->>SRP: catch(e){ error = e.message }
    U->>SRP: 点击"重试"按钮
    SRP->>SRP: refresh() 重新走首屏加载流程
